ading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BlueCollar.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BlueCollar.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BlueCollar.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BlueCollar.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/BlueCollar.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><em><a href=\"https://falconercycles.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Falconer</a>, <a href=\"https://www.btchnbikes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">BTCHN Bikes</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/bluecollarbikes916/\" target=\"_blank\">Blue Collar Bikes</a></em></p>\n<p><strong>Donate to the <a href=\"https://givebutter.com/buildersforbuilders\" target=\"_blank\">Sierra Buttes Trail Stewardship</a> for a chance to win!</strong></p>\n<p><em>The SBTS and <a href=\"https://echoscomm.com/\"> ECHOS Communications </a> powers Builders for Builders with gracious support from <a href=\"https://www.paulcomp.com/\">Paul Components</a>, <a href=\"https://www.whiteind.com/\">White Industries</a>, <a href=\"https://www.wtb.com/\"> WTB </a>, and the frame builder community.</em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2024-builders-for-builders/\">2024 Sierra Buttes Trail Stewardship Builders for Builders Fundraiser</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"b4225ddfa43567096a6979644fbcfdb0a8c5b86abd6a3a91f331a8e009767953","category":"Cycling"}